videos.headline: Hamby gets back-to-back transition layups late in the first
videos.description: Aces force back-to-back turnovers, resulting in a couple Dearica Hamby layups.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Hamby gets back-to-back transition layups late in the first) 2020/08/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson goes right past the defense for the bucket
videos.description: A'ja Wilson uses her quickness to blow right by the defender for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Wilson goes right past the defense for the bucket) 2020/08/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson drops dime to Allen for the basket
videos.description: A'ja Wilson and Lindsay Allen run the backdoor to perfection, resulting in a wide-open layup for Allen.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Wilson drops dime to Allen for the basket) 2020/08/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young gets circus shot to fall
videos.description: Jackie Young fights through three defenders then gets the basket to go while falling to the floor.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Young gets circus shot to fall) 2020/08/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hamby's daughter joins Rodgers for postgame interview
videos.description: While Holly Rowe interviews Sugar Rodgers, Dearica Hamby's daughter Amaya joins in and finishes it with a high five.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Hamby's daughter joins Rodgers for postgame interview) 2020/08/15
